Creating an influence plan

Quiz 1: How can you stay engaged and happy in your career over the next few years
Quiz 2: What are yourr top three gaols
Queiz 3: What kind of learning resources do you need to accomplish your goals
Quiz 4: To accomplish your goals, what relationships do you need in your radar

	* Take time to continually foster relationships
	-> Five minutes every week for a quick email update

---

Getting past "NO"

participant A: asks for something
participant B: Says No
participant A: responds with diagnostic question
participant B: gives a reason
participant A: labels and mirrors
participant A: Reframes


